{"tid":2209353,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"我第一日返PT，俾人針對","createTime":"2020-09-19T14:49:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-20T15:23:29.000Z","uid":52764,"like":8,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"050ea2402a36424f6421219b23a2b6d56b3ac45f","tid":2209353,"uid":52764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T14:49:47.000Z","msg":"我今年十八歲，之前申請左做馬會既電話投注事務助理，<br />\n呢個係我第一次返PT<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n返工之前，大家都俾我好多期望，同埋好多教誨，<br />\n首先daddy mammy、uncle john同埋auntie daisy就響我返工之前一日教我：「你一定要熱愛你既工作，要學識敬業樂業。」<br />\n仲有我最愛既李老師同陳老師就提醒我，「你一定要無時無刻都要專心響你既工作上面，唔可以偷懶 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />！」<br />\n我作為一個乖乖仔，咁我一定聽佢地既話啦，<br />\n就咁樣，我就出門口，開始左我做PT既日子。<br />\n<br />\n咁今日第一日返工啦，我返1115-1615，咁我十點半就入去。<br />\n先生教我地唔可以遲到，如果唔係就唔乖架啦。<br />\n首先果個組長哥哥，一見到我第一日返工就叫我食飯先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，<br />\n咁我拿拿臨用左10分鐘就食完，<br />\n仲有20分鐘，咁我諗住立即搵返組長快d報到，然之後開始做野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，<br />\n因為食完野成個人都抖完氣啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，係時候要全力工作 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n同埋我覺得，我返工係為左要服務人羣，<br />\n要為廣大馬迷服務，效率係好緊要，<br />\n我寧願快D食飯都唔想令佢地買唔到馬買唔到波唔開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n雖然個組長哥哥好好人，但係佢同我講：「仲有20分鐘喎！」<br />\n咁我就話：「我真係食完飯啦。」<br />\n佢點都唔肯俾我做野住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，<br />\n我真係好唔開心，個心唔係好舒服<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，<br />\n一來我想做野，你又唔俾我做，<br />\n二來我聽到D組長哥哥組長姐姐都響度細聲講大聲笑，<br />\n我唔知佢地笑緊邊個啦，<br />\n但係我好唔開心囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，一間大機構D人唔係應該專業D架咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？<br />\n<br />\n到我真係開工啦，有個AUNTIE睇實我，<br />\n佢不單止好好人，又好肯幫我，<br />\n同時最感動既，係佢好PROUD OF佢自己既工作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n佢同我講，顧客、顧員同埋馬會都係一家人，<br />\n主任是我爸，組長是我媽，我聽馬會既話，電話投注是我家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n我好似明又好似唔明，佢用一句簡單既說話同我講：<br />\n「你要聽馬會既話，照馬會既指示做野，做馬會既好職員。」<br />\n我真係好感動。<br />\n我決定左要為廣大馬迷服務奉獻出自己既一份力量，<br />\n我要將有限既時間，投入到無限既為馬迷服務之中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n咁過左一陣，佢帶我去廁所，順便介紹佢D FD俾我識。<br />\n佢地一開始就話：「放心，我地會照住你既，有你著數！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」<br />\n不過我就話：「去完廁所，我要快D返位，要為廣大馬迷戰鬥呀！」<br />\n咁我行出廁所門口果陣，我好似聽到D恥笑聲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n我唔知點解，但係我覺得好嬲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />！<br />\n我返工做野係天經地義！唔係去蛇王識朋友架 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />！<br />\n呢班人都唔係全心全意為馬迷既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />！<br />\n不過咁，我就係知道每一個地方都有D咁既懶人，<br />\n所以我已經著左成人尿片，就算全日唔去廁所都唔驚啦。<br />\n因為，為廣大馬迷服務係我既光榮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />！<br />\n<br />\n咁我返去我個位度啦，我見到個場景嚇左一跳 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，<br />\n乜 咁 多 人 唔 響 個 位 度 既 ? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我一返到黎既時候，個組長哥哥就提我要六個去一個，<br />\n但係依家完全係兩回事喎！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我同另一個組長姐姐講：「搞錯啊，佢地咁多個都唔跟規矩呀！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」<br />\n組長姐姐就話：「OK我會處理」<br />\n話就話會處理，佢地班人返黎果時，個組長姐姐就完全冇出聲。<br />\n成班人都唔乖、唔跟紀律既，點俾到顧客好既服務呢？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我同個AUNTIE講：「搞錯啊，佢地咁多個都唔守規矩既？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」<br />\n佢同我講：「算啦，唔使理佢地。 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」<br />\n我嬲嬲地，有少少想喊：「咁係呀嘛！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」<br />\n我見到成班人響到陰陰咀笑 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，<br />\n話乜野個細佬仔唔識做，乜野「正義能」，「煩HEIGHT」（PS：我唔識講粗口，個音大致係咁） <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我隔黎個妹妹（都係新人）仲要同個FD話：「我隔離個新仔正一小學雞，你同阿偉佢地講，包笑到佢地碌地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。」<br />\n我更加唔開心。 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n去到收工，就梗係拍卡先啦，<br />\n之後見到好多人未拍卡就走去廁所，<br />\n我就同個主任姐姐報串（PS：我讀書果陣成日同老師講D同學抄功課） <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，<br />\n咁個主任姐姐就同我一齊行去廁所門口趕人，<br />\n我聽到成班同事話：「死傻仔！」 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n走果時聽到有個染金毛既飛仔，<br />\n同佢D FD話今日有個新人好「岸溝」 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一聽就知道講緊我。 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我真係好嬲！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\">我想講：我 冇 做 錯 到 ！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong>"},{"pid":"350d4bbcb20bb4c3dc8ccc96eb0013392df13edb","tid":2209353,"uid":76747,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T14:51:25.000Z","msg":"TLDR"},{"pid":"a2f35542bfd0ddef20a0c25c2b89793b1b72712c","tid":2209353,"uid":63113,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T14:52:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wFos7Fw.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwFos7Fw.gif&h=1292dead&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2e51681615092c61630d87a2516491847543430b","tid":2209353,"uid":52764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"350d4bbcb20bb4c3dc8ccc96eb0013392df13edb","tid":2209353,"uid":76747,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T14:51:25.000Z","msg":"TLDR"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T14:53:22.000Z","msg":"我第一日返ＰＴ，俾人笑，俾人針對，但係我覺得自己冇做錯，點解佢地要咁對我？　"},{"pid":"12850d0978a45abfe196281a24e41d151fdef0ce","tid":2209353,"uid":360320,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T14:57:00.000Z","msg":"唔開心咗好耐,睇完笑番<br />\nthanks"},{"pid":"ac89001d360a768f37f8bf650abf02ea3ad43adc","tid":2209353,"uid":52764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"12850d0978a45abfe196281a24e41d151fdef0ce","tid":2209353,"uid":360320,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T14:57:00.000Z","msg":"唔開心咗好耐,睇完笑番<br />\nthanks"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T15:00:30.000Z","msg":"認真架"},{"pid":"e64e400c7ec3abd96ea1b0a54cede5a3a847d11c","tid":2209353,"uid":56467,"like":6,"dislike